	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://www.ebay.co.uk/itm/SUPER-NINTENDO-UNIVERSAL-IMPORT-GAME-ADAPTER-CARTRIDGE-SNES-UK-Converter-Cart-/362001222678?hash=item5448f44c16:g:tnoAAOSw7s5XhnlH" class="postlink">There are things like this</a> where you put a game from your region to fool the CIC and game from another region to play. <br />Not all PAL games will work in 60Hz, some check the 50/60 setting of the machine and refuse to run if it isn't what is expected. Only patching the check or modding the machine helps with that.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
